--- !u!114 &2087757544
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 2087757542}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 630b4df3f64654b9d8f5fd62ee0318c0, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  textDisplay: {fileID: 1184928204}
  sentences:
  - 'RUE: (THIS presence I-) Huh? Who are you?'
  - '???: What? C''mon. How could you not know me? We''ve been chatting for a while
    now.'
  - 'RUE: The whispers...  Was it you?'
  - '???: I just wanted to get along with my body. Is that a crime?'
  - 'RUE: What do you want? Why are you following me?'
  - '???: ... As your shadow I''m quite offended being questioned just for existing. '
  - 'RUE: My... Shadow'
  - "SHADOW: Yesss\u2026 The breath of peace you've always needed from the lies you're
    being fed. A manifestation of everything you chose to run away from."
  - 'RUE: Lies?'
  - 'SHADOW: Oh, don''t act innocent. Even if you may have partially lost your memory,
    I''ve clearly seen how everything clicked the moment you set foot near that forest. '
  - 'SHADOW: You are nothing but a failure who couldn''t deal with their choices
    and instead gave their soul to a fallen God in order to fulfil a long overdue
    chain.'
  - 'RUE: I don''t know of this God you''re speaking of and whatever their plans
    may be. Being a failure is not a bad thing. '
  - 'SHADOW: Pfft. You are the biggest I''ve seen to date. Look at you. Already accustomed
    to being a keeper.'
  - 'RUE: Keeper? What do you mean by that? Why the riddles?'
  - 'SHADOW: This whole world is one big training ground in Oneiro''s little game
    for failures-...'
  - 'RUE: *Hearing whispers* "Worthless" , "Insignificant" '
  - 'SHADOW: ...- Who couldn''t stand up for themselves and chose to end it-...'
  - 'RUE: *Tearfully* STOP!!! I didn''t WANT to do it... I just wanted it all to
    stop...'
  - 'SHADOW: *Smirking* And you think ending ends it?'
  - 'SHADOW: I know how you feel. We''re more alike than you realize. '
  - 'SHADOW: You can choose to fight. It''s not too late to let them know your worth.
    I can lend you the strength. Together we''ll rid you from being Oneiro''s puppet
    once and for all!'
  - 'RUE: *Voices intensify* "Give it to me or else-...", "Oh look! She''s speaking
    in gestures again, fucking weirdo"'
  - 'RUE: ...'
  - 'RUE: Will I get to see my parents one last time?'
  - 'SHADOW: Yeah yeah, now, all we need is for you to head to my tower so that we
    can become one.'
  - 'SHADOW: Just go through the portal and let the voids fill your heart. Simple,
    no?'
  typingspeed: 0.07
  continueButton: {fileID: 906325458}
  DialogueManager: {fileID: 642325927}
